理身體 之後就好左好多"},{"pid":"11e19ac0aa9d81771a7b8c95c5914af1722cad51","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇西醫死得仲快 生cancer 都救唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西醫廢=中醫係真有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先已經講過西醫唔係完美但通過到對照實驗，係咁重複好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊 我知中醫有料 因為我有個朋友個親戚以前生cancer 睇西醫睇左幾耐都無用又洗左勁多錢都醫唔好 之後去睇中醫 去調理身體 之後就好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醫到cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地生活係同一個時空 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569f5eabd298365b0de1e6a285c60e55460a7861","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又黎依d post，上個月先有條撚樣講中醫係垃圾討論到俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7907c5c174e2c0b2e3d11bce0e2590cf0d12093b","tid":199473,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬有無諗過你飲嘅藥水點整出嚟"},{"pid":"a4bdb4c7e8f5709f527f5af798357260746f18b0","tid":199473,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"中醫算唔算偽科學？<br />\n我諗大概都算 因為好多野都prove唔到<br />\n不過又用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講 中醫好多都係根據前人所知<br />\n亦即係統計 我諗點都屬於統計學<br />\n<br />\n有朝一日 中醫將會一步一步畀人prove到<br />\n屠呦呦嗰單 已經係絕佳例子<br />\n所以 我諗 中醫將會成為科學<br />\n而依架 暫時未係<br />\n到所有野數據化 就會係<br />\n<br />\n利申 撐中醫"},{"pid":"3c5a4da5acb2d67216b0cb8e49db69f8ad8e298e","tid":199473,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"其實跌打算唔算中醫？（真係想知）<br />\n<br />\n如果算，我極度唔撚認同你<br />\n如果唔算就冇咩特別意見"},{"pid":"95ade34e917c734ea9b36c59ede2b1224a6f9838","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫算唔算偽科學？<br />\n我諗大概都算 因為好多野都prove唔到<br />\n不過又用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有朝一日 中醫將會一步一步畀人prove到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屠呦呦嗰單 已經係絕佳例子</span><br />\n所以 我諗 中醫將會成為科學<br />\n而依架 暫時未係<br />\n到所有野數據化 就會係<br />\n<br />\n利申 撐中醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我冇記錯，佢引用果本原典有四十幾種藥方，其中有：<br />\n「抱著隻雞，然後等佢嗚叫」、「將蜘蛛放係飯團入面，食左佢」就可以醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 根本就係大包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f38cf516922ab37a42c5eb5b97e9c6d316ceba","tid":199473,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"醫得好病我理撚得你咩柒閪窿科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b133c455c565106f6f576e208a136263fa59b455","tid":199473,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>存在即是道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算你話佢係偽科學<br />\n都改變唔到佢係存在呢個事實<br />\n如果真係無效 佢又點解存在呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ae26808357d63ca0150dce5a2f97a4d581d52","tid":199473,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇西醫死得仲快 生cancer 都救唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西醫廢=中醫係真有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先已經講過西醫唔係完美但通過到對照實驗，係咁重複好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊 我知中醫有料 因為我有個朋友個親戚以前生cancer 睇西醫睇左幾耐都無用又洗左勁多錢都醫唔好 之後去睇中醫 去調理身體 之後就好左好多</blockquote><br />\nYes 我姨媽個姑姐個阿嫲個仔都係咁。"},{"pid":"385120550f92e0889fdc5fd4c6efca4c0a7785c8","tid":199473,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"中醫治療就溫和d 對身體傷害唔大<br />\n主要係調理好身體黎醫病<br />\n想即時有效就梗係西醫<br />\n邊有咩偽科學 反上腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731b7825f0a15fff63521bf044104ed57eed4882","tid":199473,"uid":89036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"Op讀中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cca34714ad44d2b9e284f773038f5a9cf76efd","tid":199473,"uid":90520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中醫算唔算偽科學？<br />\n我諗大概都算 因為好多野都prove唔到<br />\n不過又用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有朝一日 中醫將會一步一步畀人prove到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屠呦呦嗰單 已經係絕佳例子</span><br />\n所以 我諗 中醫將會成為科學<br />\n而依架 暫時未係<br />\n到所有野數據化 就會係<br />\n<br />\n利申 撐中醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我冇記錯，佢引用果本原典有四十幾種藥方，其中有：<br />\n「抱著隻雞，然後等佢嗚叫」、「將蜘蛛放係飯團入面，食左佢」就可以醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 根本就係大包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔係用嗰個乜青素黎拎獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nProve咗中草藥 係有科學support啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n所以先拎到諾貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係"},{"pid":"e874fe10fa27fceed6eb5c188a250bf03f638841","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫算唔算偽科學？<br />\n我諗大概都算 因為好多野都prove唔到<br />\n不過又用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有朝一日 中醫將會一步一步畀人prove到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屠呦呦嗰單 已經係絕佳例子</span><br />\n所以 我諗 中醫將會成為科學<br />\n而依架 暫時未係<br />\n到所有野數據化 就會係<br />\n<br />\n利申 撐中醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我冇記錯，佢引用果本原典有四十幾種藥方，其中有：<br />\n「抱著隻雞，然後等佢嗚叫」、「將蜘蛛放係飯團入面，食左佢」就可以醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 根本就係大包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔係用嗰個乜青素黎拎獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nProve咗中草藥 係有科學support啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n所以先拎到諾貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係拎咗，但睇翻本原著，完全係亂尻咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ce2dadab941484f90bead4ab796f1faf79331","tid":199473,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實跌打算唔算中醫？（真係想知）<br />\n<br />\n如果算，我極度唔撚認同你<br />\n如果唔算就冇咩特別意見</blockquote><br />\n你由得樓主條傻仔斷腳嗰陣時睇西醫物理治療啦<br />\n樓主老嗰陣時一定要堅守信仰<br />\n唔好搵偽科學跌打醫生幫手"},{"pid":"ed09b60bbf4f77cffd61014db3606fe2b2cb405e","tid":199473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Op讀中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n您讀中醫？"},{"pid":"e25c098d2e03888e86eddcfc49ea06c1d1615031","tid":199473,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3523829be1ecbdcfe51348300cd396f699795","tid":199473,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"係偽科學咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我傷風感冒都係睇中醫飲一兩劑藥就好得哂，理得佢科唔科學，有用就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要係飲完佢啲藥唔會眼訓，仲可以精精神神，唔似好多西藥會眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得西醫就係衰係依樣野到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然大病果啲西醫一定比中醫好同有用係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d26956877e916bc3f82f4c8e03075dcd2d5bfc","tid":199473,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8cfeb2e772c170aa6ce107fcf5866c5cc598487","tid":199473,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"樓主條撚樣去咗邊"},{"pid":"0601f1e8ac765982c5eae65b57bd8843d73c8609","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nProponents often cite acupuncture&rsquo;s ancient heritage as a virtue, but it is more of a vice. Acupuncture was developed in a pre-scientific culture, before anything significant was understood about biology, the normal functioning of the human body or disease pathology. The healing practices of the time were part of what is called philosophy-based medicine, to be distinguished from modern science-based medicine. Philosophy-based systems began with a set of ideas about health and illness and based their treatments on those ideas. The underlying assumptions and the practices derived from them were never subjected to controlled observation or anything that can reasonably be called a scientific process.<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://sciencebasedmedicine.org/reference/acupuncture/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsciencebasedmedicine.org%2Freference%2Facupuncture%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3cc8024d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sciencebasedmedicine.org/reference/acupuncture/</a><br />\n<br />\n辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1296c08f58a59654fca7da4ce784f84a0f6d086b","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫同風水算命一撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc8c2eb9cd47e6638b41608236a5b7f4f5c5aa1","tid":199473,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n針灸只係對痛症有作用，對其他病寶全經唔起科學實證"},{"pid":"ae4b96c87f3c0eca594e8fe7fd71584c4fee3621","tid":199473,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"不過西醫有啲真係只解決病徵，好似傷風感冒咁，只係等你舒服啲，完全冇醫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25d320de52950ade0eb14543cc835dc86e671db","tid":199473,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n針灸只係對痛症有作用，對其他病寶全經唔起科學實證</blockquote><br />\n即係用啲針 針尻啲神經線<br />\n令個受針者 feel 唔到痛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392b5fb2d87c60a42aa8a2d05f83977cfd410f00","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過西醫有啲真係只解決病徵，好似傷風感冒咁，只係等你舒服啲，完全冇醫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西醫治標等你舒服啲，再由人體機能自我修複，好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔喺萬能，但至少好過中醫冇科學實驗亂咁比藥你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed070e67d05c1465f102697060b7460d40c26aed","tid":199473,"uid":96935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n針灸只係對痛症有作用，對其他病寶全經唔起科學實證</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTotally disagree.<br />\n<br />\nAcupuncture 對asthma, COPD, rheumatoid arthritis 之類既病都有<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Randomised control trial (RCT)</span></span> <br />\nprove 左係有用<br />\n<br />\n使唔使quote 埋paper 比你阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd8961c0ae225fba3dbf699fa9b41868043ef8c","tid":199473,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過西醫有啲真係只解決病徵，好似傷風感冒咁，只係等你舒服啲，完全冇醫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為過濾性病毒仲未有藥醫，只可以靠抵抗力～ 但都唔見得中醫可以醫得好"},{"pid":"53cde7b216df374baccd3ea7f04997cb59c89b3e","tid":199473,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主條傻仔可唔可以上網google下針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n針灸只係對痛症有作用，對其他病寶全經唔起科學實證</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTotally disagree.<br />\n<br />\nAcupuncture 對asthma, COPD, rheumatoid arthritis 之類既病都有<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Randomised control trial (RCT)</span></span> <br />\nprove 左係有用<br />\n<br />\n使唔使quote 埋paper 比你阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有嘢佐證令討論更高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇Link睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}